Benetton Group Spa [BTOM.MI] saidit reached agreement with textiles concern [GFT-GruppoFinanziario Tessile Spa] for a joint venture in the financialservices sector.    A Benetton spokeswoman said details of the accord would beoutlined at a news conference on Thursday in Milan. The Italianclothing group has targeted financial services as a sector inwhich to expand its activities.    In January, Benetton acquired a large minority stake in theItalian unit of the U.K. Financial services group PrudentialCorp PLC [PRUL.L]. Reuter&#3;